(354, 3, '2014-09-07 08:08:59', '2014-09-07 08:08:59', '<p style="color: #4b5c66;"><strong>SAN FRANCISCO, August 15, 2014</strong> -- Classcast was as an official sponsor of the WAFIC fitness conference in Western Australia, Australia. This sponsorship was the first in the new relationship with the WAFIC event; and Fitness Network. Additionally, it was the companies first major event sponsorship in the APAC market.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">"The relationship we have with Fitness Network, and WAFIC, is a natural fit for Classcast," says Stuart Guest-Smith, CEO of Classcast. "We''re excited to work with the fantastic people at Fitness Network and look forward to supporting the event in 2015".</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">"We''re committed to being an active part of the Australasia fitness community, and will continue to invest in the future," added Guest-Smith.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">The sponsorship will provide lanyards for all delegates of the event.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;"><strong>About Australian Fitness Network</strong></p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;"><span style="color: #4b4b4b;">Australian Fitness Network - or ''Network'' as it is known - was launched in 1987 to service the needs of those working in the fitness industry. Established by myself, Greg Hurst and Dr Garry Egger as the ''Fitness Leader Network'', in 1999 we became ‘</span><em style="color: #4b4b4b;">Australian Fitness Network’</em><span style="color: #4b4b4b;">, a name reflecting the expansion of the industry from consisting purely of fitness instructors, to encompassing all areas of fitness, from facility owners and managers, to gym instructors and personal trainers.</span> For additional information, visit <a title="Fitness Network" href="http://www.fitnessnetwork.com.au">www.fitnessnetwork.com.au</a></p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">Follow us @twitter.com/ozfitnetwork</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;"><strong>About Classcast</strong></p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">Classcast is the groundbreaking content publishing platform for the health, wellness and fitness industry that is reinventing the way people discover, deliver and create content. Start earning monthly recurring revenue for your content, connect directly to your customers, and deliver content anywhere anytime - to any mobile.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">For businesses all over the world - fitness professionals, therapists, educators, life coaches, rehab specialists, physiotherapists... and many more in our amazing industry!</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">Launched in October 2014, Classcast is headquartered in San Francisco and was founded by Stuart Guest-Smith and Suren Reddy. Join 1000'' of happy and growing customers today! For more information and to sign up, visit <a title="Classcast Website" href="http://www.classcast.oc">www.classcast.co.</a></p>\r\n <span style="color: #4b5c66;">Follow us @twitter.com/classcastapp</span>', 'Classcast Becomes an Official Sponsor of the WAFIC Conference in Australia ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'wafic2014', '', '', '2014-09-07 09:23:23', '2014-09-07 09:23:23', '', 0, 'http://www.classcast.co/?post_type=press&#038;p=354', 0, 'press', '', 0),
(355, 3, '2014-09-05 05:25:09', '2014-09-05 05:25:09', '', 'SponsorPanel1', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'sponsorpanel1', '', '', '2014-09-05 05:25:09', '2014-09-05 05:25:09', '', 354, 'http://www.classcast.co/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/SponsorPanel1.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(356, 3, '2014-09-05 05:49:26', '2014-09-05 05:49:26', '<p style="color: #4b5c66;">SAN FRANCISCO, August, 2014 -- Live Nation Media and Sponsorship, the sponsorship and advertising division of Live Nation Entertainment, today announced Rdio as an official sponsor on LiveNation.com and the official streaming music sponsor at Live Nation''s 2013 country music festivals. The festival partnership kicked off last weekend with Faster Horses and will continue with Watershed later this summer.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">As part of Rdio''s advertising program, they will be powering Ultimate Charts on LiveNation.com. Rdio''s sponsorship also includes advertising to music fans at Live Nation venues across the country.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">"Rdio shares our commitment to enhancing the music experience for fans," says Russell Wallach, president of Live Nation Media and Sponsorship. "We are delighted that they will be showcasing their services across LiveNation.com, in our venues, and at our country music festivals."</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">"The relationship with have with Fitness Network is  a natural fit for Classcast," says Stuart Guest-Smith, CEO of Classcast. "We''re excited to work with the best in live entertainment as it gives us a chance to engage music fans before, during and after the show."</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;"><strong>About WAFIC </strong></p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">West Australian Fitness Industry Convention (WAFIC) is the world''s leading live entertainment company comprised of four market leaders: Ticketmaster.com, Live Nation Concerts, Artist Nation Management and Live Nation Media/Sponsorship. For additional information, visit www.livenation.com/investors.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">15 - 17th August, 2014</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">Follow us @twitter.com/LiveNationInc</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;"><strong>About ClasscastC</strong></p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">Calsscast is the groundbreaking digital music service that is reinventing the way people discover, listen to, and share music. With on-demand access to over 20 million songs, Rdio connects people with music and makes it easy to search for and instantly play any song, album, artist, or playlist without ever hearing a single ad. Discover what friends, people with similar tastes, recording artists, and more are listening to in real-time and share across Twitter and Facebook. Build a digital music collection that''s available everywhere -- on the web, in-home or in-car, on tablets or mobile phones, and even offline.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">Launched in August 2010, Rdio is headquartered in San Francisco and was founded by Janus Friis, the co-creator of Skype. Currently available in 31 countries, Rdio is funded by Janus Friis through his investment entities, Atomico, and Skype. For more information and to sign up, visit www.rdio.com.</p>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Classcast is an Official Sponsor of WAFIC conference in Australia ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '354-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-05 05:49:26', '2014-09-05 05:49:26', '', 354, 'http://www.classcast.co/354-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
