site" href="http://www.classcast.oc">www.classcast.co.</a></p>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Classcast is an Official Sponsor of the WAFIC conference in Australia ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '354-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-07 08:14:11', '2014-09-07 08:14:11', '', 354, 'http://www.classcast.co/354-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(367, 3, '2014-09-07 08:35:41', '2014-09-07 08:35:41', '<p style="color: #4b5c66;">SAN FRANCISCO, August 15, 2014 -- Classcast was as an official sponsor of the WAFIC fitness conference in Western Australia, Australia. This sponsorship was the first in the new relationship with the WAFIC event; and Fitness Network. Additionally, it was the companies first major event sponsorship in the APAC market.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">"The relationship we have with Fitness Network, and WAFIC, is a natural fit for Classcast," says Stuart Guest-Smith, CEO of Classcast. "We''re excited to work with the fantastic people at Fitness Network and look forward to supporting the event in 2015".</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">"We''re committed to being an active part of the Australasia fitness community, and will continue to invest in the future," added Guest-Smith.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">The sponsorship will provide lanyards for all delegates of the event.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;"><strong>About Australian Fitness Network</strong></p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;"><span style="color: #4b4b4b;">Australian Fitness Network - or ''Network'' as it is known - was launched in 1987 to service the needs of those working in the fitness industry. Established by myself, Greg Hurst and Dr Garry Egger as the ''Fitness Leader Network'', in 1999 we became ‘</span><em style="color: #4b4b4b;">Australian Fitness Network’</em><span style="color: #4b4b4b;">, a name reflecting the expansion of the industry from consisting purely of fitness instructors, to encompassing all areas of fitness, from facility owners and managers, to gym instructors and personal trainers.</span> For additional information, visit <a title="Fitness Network" href="http://www.fitnessnetwork.com.au">www.fitnessnetwork.com.au</a></p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">Follow us @twitter.com/ozfitnetwork</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;"><strong>About Classcast</strong></p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">Classcast is the groundbreaking content publishing platform for the health, wellness and fitness industry that is reinventing the way people discover, deliver and create content. Start earning monthly recurring revenue for your content, connect directly to your customers, and deliver content anywhere anytime - to any mobile.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">For businesses all over the world - fitness professionals, therapists, educators, life coaches, rehab specialists, physiotherapists... and many more in our amazing industry!</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">Launched in October 2014, Classcast is headquartered in San Francisco and was founded by Stuart Guest-Smith and Suren Reddy. Join 1000'' of happy and growing customers today! For more information and to sign up, visit <a title="Classcast Website" href="http://www.classcast.oc">www.classcast.co.</a></p>\r\n <span style="color: #4b5c66;">Follow us @twitter.com/classcastapp</span>', 'Classcast is an Official Sponsor of the WAFIC conference in Australia ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '354-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-07 08:35:41', '2014-09-07 08:35:41', '', 354, 'http://www.classcast.co/354-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(368, 3, '2014-09-07 08:57:40', '2014-09-07 08:57:40', '<p style="color: #4b5c66;">SYDNEY, 1 September 2014 – Premier health, fitness and wellness provider Classcast (www.classcast.co), founded by two passionate fitness technology founders, has today announced the availability of a completely redesigned service, providing a faster, simpler and more effective content publishing experience.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">Additionally, the company released their new website and brand. "At Classcast we continue to improve the relationship with our customers. We feel our brand is an integral part of of this communication. The website and brand is part of the next stage in our companies life. We''re excited to see this phase, and look forward to showing the industry more in the future," says Stuart Guest-Smith, CEO of Classcast.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">This is the next step in the companies journey Aidan Green, Head of Product Design at Classcast, stated it is imperative to ensure that we provide the best tools and services for our customers - design is something at the heart of our DNA.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">“With the new Classcast, we’ve gone even further, making it simpler, faster and more visually effective to create an experience that''s unique for our industry," said Green. "We decided to specialize on the health, fitness and wellness industry, for that reason our product is built to support the range of amazing content creators out there."</p>\r\n<strong>About Classcast</strong>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">Classcast is the groundbreaking content publishing platform for the health, wellness and fitness industry that is reinventing the way people discover, deliver and create content. Start earning monthly recurring revenue for your content, connect directly to your customers, and deliver content anywhere anytime - to any mobile.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">For businesses all over the world - fitness professionals, therapists, educators, life coaches, rehab specialists, physiotherapists... and many more in our amazing industry!</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">Launched in October 2014, Classcast is headquartered in San Francisco and was founded by Stuart Guest-Smith and Suren Reddy. Join 1000'' of happy and growing customers today! For more information and to sign up, visit <a title="Classcast Website" href="http://www.classcast.oc">www.classcast.co.</a></p>\r\n <span style="color: #4b5c66;">Follow us @twitter.com/classcastapp</span>', 'Classcast - Fresh Coat of Paint with Revamped Design', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '360-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-07 08:57:40', '2014-09-07 08:57:40', '', 360, 'http://www.classcast.co/360-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
