specialists, physiotherapists... and many more in our amazing industry!</p>\n<p style="color: #4b5c66;">Launched in October 2014, Classcast is headquartered in San Francisco and was founded by Stuart Guest-Smith and Suren Reddy. Join 1000'' of happy and growing customers today! For more information and to sign up, visit <a title="Classcast Website" href="http://www.classcast.oc">www.classcast.co.</a></p>\n <span style="color: #4b5c66;">Follow us @twitter.com/classcastapp</span>', 'Classcast - Fresh Coat of Paint with Revamped Design', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '360-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-09-07 09:04:43', '2014-09-07 09:04:43', '', 360, 'http://www.classcast.co/360-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
